OL,3,CMedicinal cannabis factory to create
OL,4,Cup to 100 jobs
OL,6,FA Sydney-based medicinal cannabis
OL,7,Fcompany is set to open a manufacturing
OL,8,Fand distribution centre in the
OL,9,FScottish Borders, following an
OL,10,F#848,250 investment from South of
OL,11,FScotland Enterprise.
OL,13,FBreathe Life Sciences, which already
OL,14,Foperates in Australia, Japan, the
OL,15,FCzech Republic, and Manchester, will
OL,16,Fcreate 36 jobs at their Borders site -
OL,17,Fand the company says up to a hundred
OL,18,Froles could eventually be filled over
OL,19,Fthe next three years.
