OL,3,CMedicinal cannabis factory to create
OL,4,Cup to 100 jobs
OL,6,FThe company focusses on alternative
OL,7,Ftherapeutics and investigational
OL,8,Fmedicines, which also include MDMA and
OL,9,FPsilocybin, the natural psychedelic
OL,10,Fcomponent of 'magic mushrooms'.
OL,12,FPatient-ready cannabis-based medicines
OL,13,Fwill be created at the Borders hub and
OL,14,Fsent to both national and
OL,15,Finternational markets.
