OL,3,CMedicinal cannabis factory to create
OL,4,Cup to 100 jobs
OL,6,FCEO Sam Watson told ITV Border:
OL,7,F"Scotland has a strong history in
OL,8,Fpharmaceutical manufacturing, and the
OL,9,FBorders region is a life-sciences hub,
OL,10,Fso we're incredibly confident and
OL,11,Fhappy about the decision to invest in
OL,12,Fthe region.
OL,14,F"We're bringing local manufacturing -
OL,15,Fmade in Scotland - to supply the rest
OL,16,Fof the UK and potentially European
OL,17,Fmarkets with a product that's in high
OL,18,Fdemand. It's an industry that's moving
OL,19,Ftowards half a billion pounds a year."
