OL,3,CMedicinal cannabis factory to create
OL,4,Cup to 100 jobs
OL,6,FMedicinal cannabis was legalised in
OL,7,Fthe UK in 2018, and since then a
OL,8,F#250million market has developed, with
OL,9,Faround 80,000 patients taking cannabis
OL,10,Flegally to manage their conditions.
OL,12,FBreathe Life Sciences expects this
OL,13,Fnumber to climb above 190,000 by 2029.
OL,15,FMr Watson said: "Cannabis is really
OL,16,Fdesigned for meeting unmet patient
OL,17,Fneeds, when patients don't respond to
OL,18,Fconventional or traditional medicines.
OL,20,F"It is used typically for chronic
OL,21,Fpain, sleep anxiety and depression."
