OL,6,FThe #848,250 investment from South of
OL,7,FScotland Enterprise (SOSE) comprises a
OL,8,Fgrant of #348,250 and a #500,000 loan.
OL,10,FSOSE Interim Director of Investment,
OL,11,FBusiness and Entrepreneurship Donna
OL,12,FMarshall said: "This is exactly the
OL,13,Fkind of investment we're looking for
OL,14,Fthe region: responsible investment
OL,15,Fthat brings good quality jobs,
OL,16,Ftraining pathways, and supply chain
OL,17,Fbenefits.
